{jjdhr_heat_s}
. For each
{jjdt_coronet}
in stdin array:
.. Extract source
{jjdt_firemark}
from
{jjdt_coronet}
(first 2 base64 chars after prefix)
.. Verify source
{jjdt_firemark}
